<Body>
	<Title>合肥小庙镇一农户家中突发大火 或与用电短路有关</Title>  
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2014-5-4 14:48</ReportTime>  
	<Content>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e1">
					<Time tid="t1" type="relTime">5月4日上午十点多</Time>，
					<Location lid="l1">合肥小庙镇周章村一农户家中</Location>突发
					<Denoter did="d1" type="emergency">大火</Denoter>
				</Event>，幸好
				<Event eid="e2">在周边
					<Participant sid="s2">邻居</Participant>的帮忙下将
					<Object oid="o2">火</Object>
					<Denoter did="d2" type="operation">扑灭</Denoter>
				</Event>。火灾致使
				<Event eid="e3">
					<Participant sid="s3">农户家</Participant>
					<Denoter did="d3" type="stateChange">损失</Denoter>
					<Object sid="s3">两万元钱</Object>
				</Event>。
			</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>  
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e4" type="thoughtevent">经
					<Participant sid="s4">辖区消防部门</Participant>初步
					<Denoter did="d4" type="statement">认定</Denoter>
				</Event>，
				<Event eid="e5">
					<Location lid="l5">张师傅家</Location>
					<Denoter did="d5" type="emergency">失火</Denoter>
				</Event>可能与
				<Event eid="e6">
					<Object sid="s6">用电</Object>
					<Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">短路</Denoter>
				</Event>有关。
			</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>
	</Content>  
